It’s been awhile since I last posted -again- But lately I haven’t enjoyed posting on this account because I feel like I need to prove other instagram makeup artists my skills by posting artsy and abstract looks instead of simple everyday makeup looks. Like it’s just been unnecessary stress because of that, but now I’m once again in a good mind set and I actually enjoy doing videos again! So instead of thinking that I need to post same kind of content like others, I’ll be focusing more on doing ”plain” makeup looks that I can go out with. Rant over. —————
